{"tid":1910451,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"電影分享IG","createTime":"2020-03-04T16:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T14:52:01.000Z","uid":8286,"like":17,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"23df8292016fa9a462862e498f5c2f468c81241a","tid":1910451,"uid":8286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T16:30:25.000Z","msg":"其實細佬一直好想每一次睇完戲之後都寫啲野出嚟同人分享自己嘅感受，上個月Home Office開始之後的起心肝開咗個IG，希望可以將之前睇過嘅戲都寫低自己嘅感想同評論(主要可能係contextual少少，拍攝技巧嘅分析仲研究緊點樣入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n希望可以同咁多位巴絲打交流下唔同嘅電影同大家睇法，亦都想改善下自己寫作嘅技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該仲有好多地方需要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而我盡可能都會兩三日寫一篇出嚟(原本想一日一post，但發現時間上有啲困難，因為日頭要返工夜晚要讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n希望大家多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hk.cinema?igshid=u3ld2zdqeje8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhk.cinema%3Figshid%3Du3ld2zdqeje8&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIHO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=e1bb848f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hk.cinema?igshid=u3ld2zdqeje8</a>"},{"pid":"8ea2a7a502541e12cc478d8759abaff293591d45","tid":1910451,"uid":8286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdc14773c8f99c2fae4a1d6d64d4a5a01465b41","tid":1910451,"uid":152432,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:00:08.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好難得有人欣賞探討存在主義嘅電影<br />\n真心覺得大象同燒失樂園係年度佳作"},{"pid":"c9b72e2fed8fd5b167dc9ecd2ca1cbefd7274ba7","tid":1910451,"uid":8286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7bdc14773c8f99c2f